      <section class="intro-section">
        <h2>Why Our Process Makes the Difference</h2>
        <p>Great websites aren't built by accidentâ€”they're the result of careful planning, strategic thinking, and systematic execution. Our development process has been refined through hundreds of successful projects, eliminating guesswork and ensuring consistent, high-quality results.</p>
        
        <p>From the initial discovery call to post-launch optimization, every step is designed to maximize your investment while minimizing risks. We believe in complete transparency, which is why we've documented our entire process so you know exactly what to expect at every stage.</p>
